node.text:

node.text:
📣 Have you heard the news?! My dear friend and co-creator, Agnes @hellowonderful_co , wrote a book!!!! Inspired by this page, it’s packed with 50 easy play and learn activities using items we probably have just lying around the house or in the recycling bin 🥳. I’m so incredibly proud of Agnes for making this dream come true ✨✨✨. 
•
➡️ Tap the link in profile for more information and to PREORDER Recycle And Play now 🤗. (xx Myriam, @mothercould)
.
.
.
